Detailed Description

cvmx_usbc::_gintmsk

Core Interrupt Mask Register (GINTMSK)

This register works with the Core Interrupt register to interrupt the application. When an interrupt bit is masked, the interrupt associated with that bit will not be generated. However, the Core Interrupt (GINTSTS) register bit corresponding to that interrupt will still be set. Mask interrupt: 1'b0, Unmask interrupt: 1'b1
